snippet.title: Truth Behind Income Tax Dept Raids and Seizure of Black Money in Bulk

localized.description:
Watch India TV's special report to know the truth behind Income tax department raids and seizure of black money in bulk..
Hundreds of crore cash which include old Rs 500 and Rs 1000 notes and new Rs 2000 notes have been seized in the raids by Income tax department across the country while people are standing in queues outside banks and ATMs. Many corrupt bank employees have been suspended and transferred for converting black money into white.
